Use this class to record to an [[AudioClip|audio clip]] using a connected microphone.
To get a list of connected microphone(s) use [[Microphone.devices|Microphone.devices]].
To start a recording session, use [[Microphone.Start|Microphone.Start]] with a device name (or null/empty string to use the default device).
To stop a recording, use [[Microphone.End|Microphone.End]] with the device ID you used when starting a recording.